net.sourceforge.JDash.waba
Class Setup

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.JDash.waba.Setup

public class Setup
extends java.lang.Object

This singleton class loads and holds all the setup and config settings for this dashboard. When the dashboard main window is started, it will init this class. This class will then initialize itself, and install itself at the lone Setup singleton.
